How to run the server:
    php -S localhost:80 server.php

Notes:
    - All countries follow ISO-3166-alpha-2 format guidelines

GET /search?q={string}
    - Search NPOs that match {string}
    - {string} must be at least 3 chars in length
    - {string} must be url encoded

GET /portugal/abraco
    - Retrieve an NPO by slug

GET /causes
    - Retrieve all causes

GET /causes/{cause_id}/npos
    - Retrieve npos with a cause represented by {cause_id}

POST /register
    - all fields are mandatory

POST /login
    - all fields are mandatory
